cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SY, cs.CE

The paper discusses the use of machine learning for physical problems, specifically in discovering underlying theories. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of neural networks (NN) also suggests the category of neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The iterative methodology proposed in the paper involves correlation analysis and training of NN, which can be categorized under systems and control (cs.SY) and computational engineering, finance, and science (cs.CE).
